N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4122.34 - Test of mutuel equipment

State Regulations

All tracks shall have a test, by actual operation, of the
pari-mutuel equipment before the opening of each meeting, which shall be
approved by a representative of the commission and of the State Tax
